{"tid":1698613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[周梓樂墮樓]領展CCTV多鏡頭同步全記錄","createTime":"2019-11-07T15:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T17:23:02.000Z","uid":206090,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b942ce935fa4d8321a415b739fe6d3e253b84754","tid":1698613,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7AIDRX8nu9k?t=4978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7AIDRX8nu9k%3Ft%3D4978&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=849783a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7AIDRX8nu9k?t=4978</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">同步所有領展的CCTV片段，分上中下為3/F 2/F G/F鏡頭。</span></span></strong><br />\n<ins><strong>影片的1:23:02  - 2/F C30鏡頭拍攝到白影 (現實時間約1:02:24 am)，有網友認為是周梓樂墮樓的一刻。</strong></ins><br />\n各位留意一點，2/F C31鏡頭在2.5/F (2及3樓之間的一層)。而3/F C34鏡頭向前看的遠處(例如出入口)是2.5/F，睇下面位置圖可以明白。<br />\n<br />\n6個鏡頭位置圖如下。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axCWYnn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxCWYnn.jpg&h=a6229df4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DE0d0AN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDE0d0AN.jpg&h=c4207897&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jxuVut9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjxuVut9.jpg&h=e0ec3b53&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n相關報導:<br />\n- 立場: 【周梓樂墮樓】分析近十小時 CCTV 未見催淚彈或警追捕 惟盲點極多尚未釋疑<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93-%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%81%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-cctv-%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%88%96%E8%AD%A6%E8%BF%BD%E6%8D%95-%E6%83%9F%E7%9B%B2%E9%BB%9E%E6%A5%B5%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E9%87%8B%E7%96%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593-%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259E%2590%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582-cctv-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%2583%259F%25E7%259B%25B2%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25B0%259A%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%2587%258B%25E7%2596%2591%2F&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=0e1c24a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593-%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%259E%2590%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582-cctv-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%2583%259F%25E7%259B%25B2%25E9%25BB%259E%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25B0%259A%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%2587%258B%25E7%2596%2591%2F&h=e8206ee8\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93-%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%81%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82-cctv-%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%88%96%E8%AD%A6%E8%BF%BD%E6%8D%95-%E6%83%9F%E7%9B%B2%E9%BB%9E%E6%A5%B5%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E9%87%8B%E7%96%91/</a></span><br />\n- RTHK: 領展公開停車場片段未見科大生出事過程<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490466-20191106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490466-20191106.htm&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqK9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=bd866835\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490466-20191106.htm&h=39ada5d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490466-20191106.htm</a></span><br />\n- 端傳媒: 科大學生墮樓疑雲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=